title: Sketchbook Folio, "Seascape with Dark Clouds and Breaking Waves", 1890–1900
medium: Pen and black ink on off-white wove paper
provenance: Anna Richards Brewster, Scarsdale, NY, 1905-1952; William T. Brewster,
creditline: Gift of the National Academy of Design from the Mrs. William T. Brewster Bequest
description: Beach in foreground with large breaking waves. Dark sky with towering clouds. Miscellaneous pen strokes in margin at top right corner, ink smudges in margin at top left corner.
